We recommended that the Local Chief Executive instruct the Municipal  Environment and Management Officer (MENRO) to: (i) intensify awareness of  the constituents on the “no segregation, no collection policy” and the “no-littering policy” of the Municipality thru creative information campaign and education activities  in schools, barangays, commercial establishments, and  private or government offices to reduce service costs incurred in bringing garbage from the source to the MRFs/Landfill; 

